* Authentication &\nAccess Controls
** Open sharing: tokens
***_ Set token expiration
***_ Metastore-level default lifetime
***_ Enable Delta Sharing externally
** OIDC Federation
***_ Short-lived OAuth tokens
***_ Recipient's identity provider JWT
***_ Eliminates long-lived credentials
** IP access lists
***_ Assign to open sharing recipients
***_ IP addresses or CIDR ranges
***_ Max 100 IP/CIDR values per recipient
***_ Unlisted IP → access denied + logged
** Least privilege
***_ CREATE SHARE, CREATE RECIPIENT
***_ USE SHARE, SET SHARE PERMISSION
***_ USE RECIPIENT
***_ Assign to groups not individuals
@endmindmap
